{"title":"人不知自己有错","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":12,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"人不知自己有错"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（蒙古谚语）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人不知自己有错，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骆驼不觉自己仰脖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有学问的人像果树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——纽纽弯弯；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愚蠢的人像竹竿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——滑滑尖尖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人在甜言上易栽跟头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马在软地上常打前失。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郝苏民辑译"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}